Geographic origin: Corona, Riverside County, California, United States
Notes on original: Specimen #1 - striped lemon, Specimen #2 - standard lemon; Sporting & Standard Types and Tree 33-1-52, From same tree. This tree has one branch with striped fruits and foliage. The rest of the tree bears standard Eureka fruit and foliage.
Name: Citrus limon: Eureka
